)]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1992\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |51 ||[[Stadionul Municipal (Sf\u00e2ntu Gheorghe)|Stadionul Municipal]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 5,200 ||[[Sf\u00e2ntu Gheorghe]]||'''[[ACS Sepsi OSK Sf\u00e2ntu Gheorghe|Sepsi Sf\u00e2ntu Gheorghe]]'''|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1930\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |52 ||[[Stadionul Concordia]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 5,123 ||[[Chiajna]]||[[CS Concordia Chiajna|Concordia Chiajna]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2007\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |53 ||[[Stadionul Anghel Iord\u0103nescu]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4,600 ||[[Voluntari]]||'''[[FC Voluntari|Voluntari]]'''|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2010\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |54 ||[[Stadionul Viitorul (Ovidiu)|Stadionul Viitorul]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4,554 ||[[Ovidiu]]||'''[[FC Viitorul Constan\u021ba|Viitorul Constan\u021ba]]'''|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2015\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |55 ||[[Stadionul Clinceni|Clinceni]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 4,500 ||[[Clinceni]]||'''[[FC Academica Clinceni|Academica Clinceni]]'''|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2011\n|}\nTeam in '''Bold''': [[Liga I]] clubs.\n\n===UEFA Elite Stadium(s)===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!#!!Stadium!!Capacity!!City!!Club!!Opened\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |1|| [[Arena Na\u021bional\u0103]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 55,634 || [[Bucharest]] || ''{{fb|ROM}}'' <br/> || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2011\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |2|| [[Stadionul Ion Oblemenco]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 30,983 || [[Craiova]] || [[CS Universitatea Craiova|Universitatea Craiova]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2017\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |3|| [[Cluj Arena]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 30,201 || [[Cluj-Napoca]] || [[FC Universitatea Cluj|Universitatea Cluj]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2011\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |4|| [[St