an]]||\u2014|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1954\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |21 ||[[Stadionul Nicolae Dobrin]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 15,000 ||[[Pite\u0219ti]]||[[FC Arge\u0219 Pite\u0219ti|Arge\u0219 Pite\u0219ti]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1964\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |22 ||[[Stadionul Cotroceni]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 14,542 ||[[Bucharest]]|| \u2014 || style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1995\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |23 ||[[Stadionul Municipal (Sibiu)|Stadionul Municipal]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 14,200 ||[[Sibiu]]||'''[[FC Hermannstadt|Hermannstadt]]'''|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1927\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |24 ||[[Stadionul O\u021belul]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 13,500 ||[[Gala\u021bi]]||[[ASC O\u021belul Gala\u021bi|O\u021belul Gala\u021bi]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1983\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |25 ||[[Stadionul Francisc von Neuman|Francisc von Neuman]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 12,700 ||[[Arad, Romania|Arad]]||[[UTA Arad]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2019\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |26 ||[[Stadionul Mircea Chivu]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 12,500 ||[[Re\u0219i\u021ba]]||[[CSM Re\u0219i\u021ba]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1926\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |27 ||[[Stadionul Tudor Vladimirescu|Tudor Vladimirescu]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 12,500 ||[[T\u00e2rgu Jiu]]||[[CS Pandurii T\u00e2rgu Jiu|Pandurii T\u00e2rgu Jiu]] / [[ACS Viitorul T\u00e2rgu Jiu|Viitorul Pandurii T\u00e2rgu Jiu]]  / [[FC U Craiova 1948|FC U Craiova]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 2019\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |28 ||[[Stadionul 1 Mai (Slatina)|Stadionul 1 Mai]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 12,000 ||[[Slatina, Romania|Slatina]]||[[CSM Slatina (football)|Slatina]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 1924\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |29 ||[[Stadionul Municipal (R\u00e2mnicu V\u00e2lcea)|Stadionul Municipal]]|| s